  <name>Mixxx (Devel)</name>
  <summary>Perform live DJ mixes</summary>
  <developer id="@mixxx@floss.social">
    <name>The Mixxx Development Team</name>
  </developer>
  <description>
    <p>
      Mixxx is a highly customizable, cross-platform DJ application that
      integrates all the tools DJs need to perform creative live mixes.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Blend songs together using automatic BPM matching and remix on the fly
      with samples, loops and hot cues.</li>
      <li>Never miss a beat with the scratchable waveform displays, volume
      normalization and accurate tempo and key detection.</li>
      <li>Spice up your mixes using high quality effects and flexible processing
      chains.</li>
      <li>Keep your music library perfectly organized with crates and
      playlists.</li>
      <li>Take a break by enabling Auto DJ with automatic crossfading.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Mixxx works with many popular DJ controllers and supports vinyl emulation
      with Serato, Traktor, and Mixvibes timecodes. Whether you're an
      experienced turntablist or just getting started, Mixxx has you covered.
    </p>
  </description>
